<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.9.4">
<l>kulantā ṉettaṉaiyum piṟantēyiṟan teyttoḻintēṉ</l>
<l>nalantā ṉoṉṟumilēṉ nallatōraṟañ ceytumilēṉ</l>
<l>nilantōy nīḷmukilcēr neṟiyārttiru vēṅkaṭavā</l>
<l>valantēṉ vantaṭaintē ṉaṭiyēṉaiyāṭ koṇṭaruḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having been born [and] having died in every [kind of] clan,</l>
<l rend="indent">I withered and weakened.</l>
<l>I do not have even one virtue; I did not even perform one good moral deed.</l>
<l>You of Tiruvēṅkaṭam full of paths with long billows [of mist]</l>
<l rend="indent">that touch the earth,</l>
<l>I, who suffers, came [here and] took refuge;</l>
<l rend="indent">be gracious, receiving me, your servant, in service.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
